               :abstract-glyph-of      jis-x0212:0x5F59  .
    rep.cns11643-2:0x715E
               :abstract-glyph-of     cns11643-2:0x715E  .
    rep.gb12345:0x7475
               :abstract-glyph-of        gb12345:0x7475  .
    a.big5:0xF96F
           :abstract-character-of           big5:0xF96F  .
    rep.daikanwa:37362
               :abstract-glyph-of       daikanwa:37362   .

